ActTobacco and Vaping Products Act
SubjectRegulations Excluding Certain Vaping Products Regulated Under the Food and Drugs Act from the Application of the Tobacco and Vaping Products Act
PrecisRegulations Excluding Certain Vaping Products in Order to ensure that the application of the TOBACCO AND VAPING PRODUCTS ACT, FOOD AND DRUG ACT and their regulations, on vaping products regulated under the FDA, is representative of their associated harms while achieving the purposes of the TOBACCO AND VAPING PRODUCTS ACT.
